    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん！　ここが私達の教室だよ\n休日で誰もいないから、遠慮しないで入って入って！",
      "startTime": 4.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3900.0000000000005,
          "startTime": 8.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お、お邪魔しまーす……\n部外者が勝手に入って怒られないかな？",
      "startTime": 12.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、ちゃんと理事長と生徒会長の\n許可は取ってあるから",
      "startTime": 20.5827677091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk003.m4a",
      "text": "……と言っても、どっちも\nAqoursのメンバーなんだけどね",
      "startTime": 24.3161010425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　生徒会長さんと理事長さんがいるの！？\nす、凄いメンバー……！",
      "startTime": 31.508598314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、ここが私の席で、そっちが曜ちゃんの席\nあっちが梨子ちゃんの席だよ",
      "startTime": 39.0576408069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk005.m4a",
      "text": "私達は毎日ここで授業を受けて、放課後になると\nスクールアイドル部の部室に集まるの",
      "startTime": 45.2243074735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "スクールアイドル部って、千歌ちゃんが立ち上げた\n部活なんだよね？",
      "startTime": 51.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk006.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　最初は一人だったけど、曜ちゃんが入って\nくれてね。そこになんと梨子ちゃんが転校してきて！",
      "startTime": 57.4291144689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk007.m4a",
      "text": "しかも梨子ちゃんはピアノやっててね、作曲出来る人が\n必要だったから、もうこれは運命だ～って思ったの！",
      "startTime": 66.0291144689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、誘っても誘っても断られちゃって～\n最後の方なんて、目が合っただけでごめんなさいって",
      "startTime": 74.7291144689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは、そうなんだ。Aqoursも\n最初から順風満帆だった訳じゃないんだね",
      "startTime": 84.5666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、最初のライブの時も、一年生と三年生が\n加入する時も、東京に遠征した時も……",
      "startTime": 93.0792524021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk010.m4a",
      "text": "大変なことが一杯あって、それを乗り越える度に\n私達の絆は、強くなっていったんだと思う",
      "startTime": 101.6792524021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに一生懸命打ち込んで\nみんな凄いね",
      "startTime": 108.3333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "大変なことが一杯あったのに\n千歌ちゃんはどうしてそんなに頑張れたの？",
      "startTime": 113.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk011.m4a",
      "text": "辞めちゃいそうになった時はあったよ\nでも、みんなと……憧れのスクールアイドルがいたから",
      "startTime": 120.1736739477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk012.m4a",
      "text": "その人達は、私と同じような\nどこにでもいる普通の高校生だけど……",
      "startTime": 128.5736739477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk013.m4a",
      "text": "かっこ良くて、可愛くて、キラキラ輝いてて……\n気付いたら私もこの人達みたいに輝きたいって思ってた",
      "startTime": 136.6736739477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk014.m4a",
      "text": "私も仲間と一緒に、自分だけの景色を探して走りたい\n走り続けたい、って思ったの",
      "startTime": 145.7070072811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ち、ちょっと分かるかも\n私にも憧れのアイドルがいるから",
      "startTime": 153.8999912262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "憧れを胸に、夢中で、全力で、青春を懸けて……\nだからスクールアイドルはこんなにも眩しいんだね",
      "startTime": 165.2333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "教えてくれてありがとう、おかげで前より\nAqoursのことが分かった気がするよ",
      "startTime": 174.0333204906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、お礼を言うのはまだ早いよ～？\nここはまだ一ヶ所目なんだから！",
      "startTime": 180.2147353174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk016.m4a",
      "text": "ここから二ヶ所目、三ヶ所目と回って\n私達の普段の活動を体験してもらっちゃうからね！",
      "startTime": 186.1480686507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uraclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uraclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_02-chk017.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、Aqours体験ツアー、どんどん行くよー！",
      "startTime": 190.1147353174,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5985.247898099999,
          "startTime": 196.0999832155
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiuracoast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiuracoast-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiuracoast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiuracoast-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
